answerText: HDL [or high-density lipoprotein; prompt on cholesterol][10]  Cholesterol, like testosterone, is one of these compounds with four cycloalkane rings.  Anabolic types of these compounds can help build muscle but are banned by pretty much every major sports organization worth anything.

subject: Science
question: Question: Some studies have looked into giving people with low levels of this substance injections of ApoA-1 Milano. For 10 points each: [10] Identify this substance, which ideally is at levels over 60 grams per litre in the blood. It is also called "good cholesterol."
